[[Image:Chorizo1.jpg|thumb|right|Chorizo]]
'''Chorizo''' is a type of [[Cookbook:Pork|pork]] [[Cookbook:Sausage|sausage]] made in [[Cookbook:Cuisine of Spain|Spain]]. A similar sausage, '''chouriço''', comes from [[Cookbook:Cuisine of Portugal|Portugal]].

It typically has a red colour from the use of [[Cookbook:Paprika|paprika]] in its preparation and is usually sold ready to eat, although it can also be used as an ingredient. 

