I rewrote an earlier version of this page that said that the Dragon was one of the easiest Sicilian systems to play. While the general themes are easy to understand, the sharpness of the variation makes it a very dangerous line for both players and I wouldn't say it's easy to learn all the myriad pitfalls. I also elaborated on the basic plans for both sides. [[User:MadeofPlants|MadeofPlants]] 21:29, 17 January 2007 (UTC)
